== 结构 ==
eIF4E含有一个由8条反平行β链组成的弯曲的[[β折叠|β折叠]]片以及三个几乎平行于β折叠片顶部链的[[α螺旋|α螺旋]]。eIF4E识别帽子的工作就由7-甲基-[[鸟嘌呤|鸟嘌呤]]和[[吲哚|吲哚]]基团之间的堆积来完成。该堆积由两个绝对保守的[[色氨酸|色氨酸]]残基，依靠三个类Watson-Crick[[氢键|氢键]]和[[范德华力|范德华力]]同第三个保守色氨酸联系起来。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Marcotrigiano J, Gingras AC, Sonenberg N, Burley SK|title=Cocrystal structure of the messenger RNA 5' cap-binding protein (eIF4E) bound to 7-methyl-GDP|journal=Cell|volume=89|year=1997|pages=951-61|pmid=9200613}}</ref>

[[磷酸化|磷酸化]]作用可以调控eIF4E的活性。例如[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]eIF4E的209位的[[丝氨酸|丝氨酸]]的磷酸化可增强eIF4E同加帽mRNA的结合并稳固eIF4E和eIF4G间的相互作用。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Waskiewicz AJ, Johnson JC, Penn B, Mahalingam M, Kimball SR, Cooper JA|title=Phosphorylation of the cap-binding protein eukaryotic translation initiation factor 4E by protein kinase Mnk1 in vivo|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-and-cellular-biology_1999-03_19_3/page/1871|journal=Mol Cell Biol|volume=19|year=1999|pages=1871-80|pmid=10022874}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Pyronnet S, Imataka H, Gingras AC, Fukunaga R, Hunter T, Sonenberg N|title=Human eukaryotic translation initiation factor 4G (eIF4G) recruits mnk1 to phosphorylate eIF4E|journal=EMBO J|volume=18|year=1999|pages=270-9|pmid=9878069}}</ref>但也有人认为该位点的磷酸化并不影响蛋白质的[[翻译_(遗传学)|翻译]]过程。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=McKendrick L, Morley SJ, Pain VM, Jagus R, Joshi B|title=Phosphorylation of eukaryotic initiation factor 4E (eIF4E) at Ser209 is not required for protein synthesis in vitro and in vivo|journal= Eur J Biochem|volume=268|year=2001|pages=5375-85|pmid=11606200}}</ref>

